=== 作曲 ===
演奏之外，賀夫也從事作曲，目前已有一首大提琴協奏曲{{efn|為{{tsl|en|Steven Isserlis|史蒂芬·伊瑟利斯}}所寫，於2007年3月首演。}}、三重奏（為短笛、倍低音管與鋼琴）、彌撒作品<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/core/Content/displayPrintable.jhtml?xml=/arts/2007/01/21/svhough21.xml&site=6&page=0 |title=With apologies to Bartok |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |date=2007-01-21 |accessdate=2015-06-18 |archive-date=2012-05-30 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120530160658/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/core/Content/displayPrintable.jhtml?xml=/arts/2007/01/21/svhough21.xml&site=6&page=0 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、歌曲、四首鋼琴奏鳴曲，以及逾卅首小品<ref name=discs/>等。

